==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Franklin stove
<hw>Frank"lin stove`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A kind of open stove
introduced by <person>Benjamin <ets>Franklin</ets></person>, the
peculiar feature of which was that a current of heated air was directly
supplied to the room from an air box; -- now applied to other varieties
of open stoves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frankly</ent>⟦br⟧
